title: Oracle 11g Release 1 Full Version
description:
This is the full windows OS version of Oracle 11g Release 1 Database Server downloaded from the oracle website. 

My purpose for sharing it is, that this is a very heavy file i.e. of 1.7GB and difficult to download without using Downloading Software as it required authentication to download the file. If anyone is downloading the file and unfortunately the modem is de-synched at 50% then you have to download the file from the beginning as the browser do not allow download pause / resume operation.

This is the commercial software and is free to use for educational purposes.

I hope you will use it commercially at your own risk.

Good Luck! 

Download and enjoy.........



I salute the team of TPB for such a wonderful site......
